Package: SeqtometryGUI
Title: Flow cytometry like graphical user interface for single cell data analysis via Seqtometry
Version: 0.1.0
URL: https://github.com/HawigerLab/SeqtometryGUI
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Robert", "Kousnetsov", email = "robert.kousnetsov@health.slu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Daniel", "Hawiger", email = "daniel.hawiger@health.slu.edu", role = c("cph")))
Description: 
    A graphical user interface built upon the interactive Plotly charting library that interfaces with 
    R via Shiny to facilitate a flow cytometric-like workflow to analyze single cell data using signature scores.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Remotes: HawigerLab/Seqtometry
